Liverpool FC fielded a team!.
Alex Ferguson opted out of the FA Cup in order to play in the world club cup competition, Ferguson often played youth players in the early stages of the cup and could easily have played a youth team!

Jürgen made it absolutely clear "the senior squad wouldn't take any part in the replay" and yet the fans filled the stadium to its capacity!
And let's not forget, The youth team not only played well, they actually won!
